(82, 'SLV-BNG-001', 'Silver Kada Bangle', 'Bangle', 'Elevate your ethnic look with our exquisite Silver Kada Bangle, crafted from premium 950 silver that showcases exceptional purity and timeless elegance. This traditional kada design combines authentic Indian craftsmanship with contemporary aesthetics, making it the perfect accessory for weddings, festivals, and everyday celebrations. Whether you''re dressing up for a special occasion or adding a touch of sophistication to your daily attire, this sterling silver bangle is a versatile treasure that complements every wardrobe.', 15572.56, 40.43, '950 Silver', '/images/products/silver-bangle-kada-001.jpg', 1, 83, '2025-03-23', 2),
