(84, 'SLV-TOE-006', 'Silver Traditional Toe Ring', 'Toe Ring', 'Elevate your traditional look with this exquisite Silver Traditional Toe Ring, meticulously crafted from premium 925 Sterling Silver that ensures lasting brilliance and durability. This timeless piece beautifully combines authentic craftsmanship with sophisticated design, making it the perfect accessory for festivals, weddings, and everyday elegance. Adorned with intricate detailing, this toe ring celebrates the rich heritage of Indian jewellery while adding a touch of refined grace to your personal style.', 1669.42, 3.32, '925 Sterling Silver', '/images/products/silver-toe-ring-traditional-006.jpg', 1, 80, '2025-03-29', 13),
(85, 'SLV-NCK-003', 'Silver Opera Length Necklace', 'Necklace', 'Elevate your timeless elegance with our exquisite Silver Opera Length Necklace, meticulously crafted from premium 950 silver that exudes sophistication and luxury. This stunning piece, designed in the classic opera length style, is the perfect companion for special occasions, from festive celebrations and weddings to refined evening gatherings, making it an essential addition to every Indian jewellery collection. Our master craftsmen have poured their expertise into every detail, creating a necklace that seamlessly blends traditional Indian aesthetics with contemporary design, ensuring you shine with grace and cultural pride.', 11237.85, 45.22, '950 Silver', '/images/products/silver-necklace-opera-length-003.jpg', 1, 31, '2025-04-07', 9),
(86, 'SLV-HRP-001', 'Silver Bobby Pin Hair Pin', 'Hair Pin', 'Elevate your everyday hairstyle with our exquisite 925 Sterling Silver Bobby Pin, meticulously crafted to blend timeless elegance with contemporary style. This premium hair accessory showcases the lustrous beauty and purity of authentic sterling silver, making it perfect for everything from casual day-to-day wear to special occasions, weddings, and festive celebrations. Each piece is designed with meticulous attention to detail, reflecting the rich tradition of Indian silver craftsmanship while adding a sophisticated touch to your personal adornment collection.', 5987.07, 5.02, '925 Sterling Silver', '/images/products/silver-hair-pin-bobby-pin-001.jpg', 1, 10, '2025-04-11', 8),
(87, 'SLV-EAR-003', 'Silver Drop Earring', 'Earring', 'Introducing our exquisitely crafted Silver Drop Earring, meticulously designed to showcase the finest 950 sterling silver with timeless elegance. Perfect for both everyday wear and special occasions, these stunning drop earrings effortlessly elevate any ensemble with their graceful silhouette and superior silver craftsmanship. Celebrate your refined taste with a piece that embodies authentic Indian jewellery traditions, blending contemporary style with enduring quality that''s sure to become a cherished part of your collection.', 5049.8, 9.59, '950 Silver', '/images/products/silver-earring-drop-003.jpg', 1, 49, '2025-04-14', 7),
(88, 'SLV-CHN-008', 'Silver Franco Chain', 'Chain', 'Elevate your style with our exquisite Silver Franco Chain, meticulously crafted from premium 925 sterling silver that ensures lasting brilliance and durability. This intricately woven Franco design showcases exceptional craftsmanship, making it the perfect accessory for both everyday elegance and special occasions, from festive celebrations to formal events. Versatile and timeless, this sophisticated chain complements traditional as well as contemporary Indian aesthetics, making it an essential addition to every jewellery collection.', 2664.46, 16.97, '925 Sterling Silver', '/images/products/silver-chain-franco-008.jpg', 1, 27, '2025-04-22', 5),
(89, 'SLV-EAR-007', 'Silver Threader Earring', 'Earring', 'Elegantly designed Silver Threader Earrings crafted from premium 925 Sterling Silver, these versatile earrings feature delicate threader styling that gracefully adorns the earlobe with timeless sophistication. Perfect for both everyday elegance and special occasions, these earrings seamlessly complement traditional attire as well as contemporary fashion, making them an essential addition to every jewellery collection. Handcrafted with meticulous attention to detail, these Sterling Silver threaders showcase exceptional craftsmanship and lustre that reflects the authentic beauty of fine Indian jewellery.', 18627.75, 4.56, '925 Sterling Silver', '/images/products/silver-earring-threader-007.jpg', 0, 0, '2025-04-23', 7),
(90, 'SLV-BRH-004', 'Silver Geometric Brooch', 'Brooch', 'Elevate your style with our exquisite Silver Geometric Brooch, meticulously crafted from premium 999 Fine Silver that radiates timeless elegance and sophistication. This stunning piece features clean, contemporary geometric lines that seamlessly complement both traditional ethnic wear and modern outfits, making it the perfect accessory for weddings, festivals, and special occasions. Each brooch is a testament to exceptional craftsmanship, designed for the discerning Indian jewellery connoisseur who appreciates fine silver artistry and versatile, wearable luxury.', 31700.68, 19.91, '999 Fine Silver', '/images/products/silver-brooch-geometric-004.jpg', 0, 0, '2025-04-25', 4),
(91, 'SLV-BRC-005', 'Silver Bangle Style Bracelet', 'Bracelet', 'Elevate your elegance with our exquisite Silver Bangle Style Bracelet, meticulously crafted from 999 fine silver that radiates timeless beauty and authenticity. Perfect for both everyday wear and special occasions—from festive celebrations to intimate gatherings—this stunning bangle combines traditional Indian jewellery aesthetics with contemporary design. Each piece is a testament to superior craftsmanship, showcasing the lustrous purity and refined artistry that makes fine silver jewellery a cherished heirloom for generations to come.', 34796.86, 25.6, '999 Fine Silver', '/images/products/silver-bracelet-bangle-style-005.jpg', 0, 6, '2025-05-01', 3),
(92, 'SLV-NCK-005', 'Silver Pendant Chain Necklace', 'Necklace', 'Elevate your ethnic collection with our exquisite Silver Pendant Chain Necklace, meticulously crafted from premium 925 Sterling Silver that guarantees lasting brilliance and durability. This versatile pendant chain seamlessly complements both traditional ensembles and contemporary styles, making it the perfect choice for weddings, festivals, and everyday celebrations. Experience the timeless elegance and authentic craftsmanship that defines our commitment to delivering jewellery pieces worthy of your most cherished moments.', 17844.7, 54.32, '925 Sterling Silver', '/images/products/silver-necklace-pendant-chain-005.jpg', 1, 56, '2025-05-04', 9),
(93, 'SLV-HRP-002', 'Silver Clip Hair Pin', 'Hair Pin', 'Introducing our exquisite Silver Clip Hair Pin, meticulously crafted from 999 Fine Silver to add an elegant touch to your everyday look or special occasions. This beautifully designed clip-style hair pin combines traditional artisanal craftsmanship with contemporary aesthetics, perfect for adorning your hair at weddings, festivals, parties, and cultural celebrations. Elevate your personal style with this timeless piece of Indian silver jewellery that seamlessly blends sophistication with versatility.', 21188.39, 5.01, '999 Fine Silver', '/images/products/silver-hair-pin-clip-002.jpg', 1, 68, '2025-05-06', 8),
(94, 'SLV-PND-002', 'Silver Gemstone Pendant', 'Pendant', 'Experience the perfect blend of elegance and tradition with our exquisite Silver Gemstone Pendant, crafted from premium 925 Sterling Silver that promises enduring brilliance and purity. This masterfully designed piece features a radiant gemstone centerpiece that catches light beautifully, making it an ideal choice for weddings, festivals, daily wear, or special celebrations—seamlessly complementing both traditional and contemporary styles. Each pendant is meticulously handcrafted by skilled artisans, embodying the timeless sophistication that defines Indian jewellery heritage while offering versatile elegance for the modern woman.', 34278.63, 15.75, '925 Sterling Silver', '/images/products/silver-pendant-gemstone-002.jpg', 1, 67, '2025-05-07', 11),
(95, 'SLV-BNG-008', 'Silver Kada Bangle', 'Bangle', 'Elevate your traditional style with our exquisite Silver Kada Bangle, meticulously crafted from premium 999 Fine Silver that showcases authentic Indian artistry and elegance. This versatile bangle seamlessly transitions from everyday wear to special occasions, making it a perfect addition to both casual and festive outfits while complementing traditional ethnic attire beautifully. Each kada is expertly designed with precision and care, reflecting the timeless charm and cultural significance of traditional silver jewellery that every discerning jewelry connoisseur cherishes.', 1729.22, 30.71, '999 Fine Silver', '/images/products/silver-bangle-kada-008.jpg', 1, 35, '2025-05-20', 2),
(96, 'SLV-ANK-006', 'Silver Payal Anklet', 'Anklet', 'Introducing our exquisite Silver Payal Anklet, meticulously crafted from pure 999 fine silver that showcases the timeless elegance of traditional Indian jewellery design. This beautifully articulated payal is perfect for weddings, festivals, and special celebrations, adding an authentic touch of grace to your traditional attire while maintaining the lustrous brilliance that only fine silver can deliver. Each piece is expertly handcrafted to ensure premium quality and lasting beauty, making it an ideal choice for those who appreciate both cultural heritage and exceptional craftsmanship.', 9326.48, 28.15, '999 Fine Silver', '/images/products/silver-anklet-payal-006.jpg', 1, 28, '2025-05-31', 1),
(97, 'SLV-RNG-004', 'Silver Stackable Ring', 'Ring', 'Introducing our exquisite Silver Stackable Ring, meticulously crafted from 999 Fine Silver that promises timeless elegance and superior quality for the discerning buyer. This versatile piece features a contemporary stackable design, allowing you to mix and match to create your own unique combinations—perfect for everyday wear, festive celebrations, or special occasions. Each ring is a testament to our commitment to fine craftsmanship, blending traditional artistry with modern aesthetics to complement your personal style and add a touch of sophisticated sparkle to any occasion.', 9031.36, 12.46, '999 Fine Silver', '/images/products/silver-ring-stackable-004.jpg', 1, 9, '2025-06-10', 12),
(98, 'SLV-EAR-010', 'Silver Hoop Earring', 'Earring', 'Timeless elegance meets superior craftsmanship in these exquisite 925 Sterling Silver Hoop Earrings, meticulously designed to complement both traditional and contemporary styles. Perfect for every occasion—from festive celebrations to everyday sophistication—these lustrous silver hoops showcase the finest quality hallmarked sterling silver that ensures durability and lasting brilliance. Each piece reflects authentic Indian jewellery artistry, making it an essential addition to your collection that transcends seasons and trends.', 2781.48, 5.63, '925 Sterling Silver', '/images/products/silver-earring-hoop-010.jpg', 1, 11, '2025-06-10', 7),
(99, 'SLV-CHN-003', 'Silver Box Chain', 'Chain', 'Elevate your everyday style with our exquisitely crafted Silver Box Chain, meticulously designed from premium 925 Sterling Silver that promises durability and lustrous brilliance. This versatile piece features a sophisticated box link pattern that seamlessly transitions from casual daywear to special occasions, making it an essential addition to your jewellery collection. Perfect for layering or wearing solo, this authentic sterling silver chain embodies traditional Indian craftsmanship while offering the timeless elegance and purity that discerning jewellery enthusiasts truly value.', 12533.02, 10.96, '925 Sterling Silver', '/images/products/silver-chain-box-003.jpg', 1, 80, '2025-06-11', 5),
(100, 'SLV-CFL-004', 'Silver Monogram Cufflink', 'Cufflink', 'Elevate your formal wardrobe with these exquisite Silver Monogram Cufflinks, meticulously crafted from premium 925 Sterling Silver that epitomizes timeless elegance and sophistication. Perfect for weddings, business meetings, and special occasions, these personalized cufflinks showcase impeccable artisanal craftsmanship that reflects the rich heritage of Indian silver jewellery. The refined monogram detailing adds a distinctive personal touch, making these cufflinks an ideal investment piece that seamlessly complements both traditional and contemporary formal attire.', 12332.01, 9.6, '925 Sterling Silver', '/images/products/silver-cufflink-monogram-004.jpg', 0, 1, '2025-06-14', 6);
